<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, June 26 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange closed at 1,735.24 points Saturday, up 3.98 points
from Wednesday's finish.
