<HEADLINE> Defense Should Be Improved Through Science: Jiang (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The institutes should perfect policies and systems and maintain
favorable conditions to attract good students and let young
teachers with innovative ideas excel, Jiang said, adding that this
should be one of their major duties.
</P>
<P>
According to him, the armed forces as a whole should join the
effort and concentrate on building the institutes of higher
learning.
</P>
<P>
He asked PLA officers and departments at all levels to proceed
with the strategy of modernizing national defense and the military
in the next century and take the initiative to support the
development of the institutes.
</P>
<P>
