for national defense, academic research on military sciences, and
the use of scientific and technological developments for combat
readiness.
</P>
<P>
The institutes must actively provide the troops and military
departments with services in knowledge, technology and information.
</P>
<P>
The general principles and guidelines for the development of
the PLA institutes of higher learning have already been set, he
said, and asked the delegates to earnestly implement these
principles, be innovative and aggressive and continue to make new
achievements in teaching.
