boxing champion from Mongolia by knocking out Japan's Takanori
Hatakeyama in a World Boxing Association (WBA) super featherweight
fight here on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The knockout time came one minute 46 seconds into the fifth
round when the 28-year-old challenger unleashed an array of so
powerful punches that the South African referee had to stop the
fight.
</P>
<P>
