<HEADLINE> "Race Against Drugs" Held in Mexico </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, June 26 (Xinhua) -- The first athletic race "All
Together To Prevent Crime, All Together Against Drugs" was held
nationwide this morning to commemorate the international anti-drug
day.
</P>
<P>
Federal Attorney-General Jorge Madrazo gave the green light to
the five-kilometer race, held simultaneously all over the country.
